Selector:- Stand for selecting an element in different ways
Selector{
    Properties
    .
    .
    .
}
Types
Simple selector
    element(p,h1...tags), Id(#), Class(.)
Combinator selector
    Descendant( ), Child(>), Adjacent(+), General Sibling(~)   
pseudo-class selector
    :hover, :Link,:Visited, :active, 
pseudo element Selector
    ::first-letter, ::last-letter, ::before, ::after
Attribute selector
    based on html elements attribute the stylings are applied
    


